  <li>3D printed plastic body</li>
  <li>Spiral-shaped joints for bending and curling</li>
  <li>Lightweight and low-cost to build</li>
  <li>2 Nema 17 steppermotors driving the joints</li>
  <li>Joystick module for manual control</li>
  <li>Powered using adapter</li>
  <li>Microcontroller (esp32)</li>
  <li>TB6600 moter driver</li>
</ul>
    </div>
